{"tid":748342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為家居布置同老婆嘈 新婚男劏房新居吊頸亡","createTime":"2018-07-19T06:42:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-19T09:34:09.000Z","uid":41404,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"75a44a725ea60efd5babd52f2fd530266620311a","tid":748342,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T06:42:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180719/large/1531977011_0cc9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180719%2Flarge%2F1531977011_0cc9.jpg&h=cd5ff089&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男事主新婚妻傷心激動，其後需由母親陪同送院。(詹家志攝)<br />\n深水埗汝州街186號唐3樓一個劏房單位，今早10時半，一名約30歲男子被新婚妻子發現在單位內以床單上吊，救護人員接報到場證實男子死亡，警方在場撿獲遺書，正展開調查。男事主新婚妻傷心激動，其後需由母親陪同送院。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指，男事主剛於去年12月註冊結婚，但未有即時與新婚妻子同住，直至最近才物色到新居共築愛巢，但近日為劏房新居布置及金錢問題，與新婚妻子爭執，之後便失去聯絡，其妻今晨到新居尋找丈夫揭發事件。<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180719/58460892\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180719%2F58460892&d=PmFcvYDdyGly%2FsMPmmCiDY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=5527c308\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180719%2F58460892&h=bc3438c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180719/58460892</a>"},{"pid":"e8e88451087f1479121fb45cf9efc78a372555a0","tid":748342,"uid":46328,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T06:46:31.000Z","msg":"奶波魔召喚"},{"pid":"87b341cca3c2bd6d1373ac786866fe1e6ecdbcea","tid":748342,"uid":50535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T06:49:09.000Z","msg":"RIP<br 